	(text "SWITCHING & OUTPUT — FINAL SCHEMATIC\n\nRELAY LOGIC (from FROZEN_SPEC.md):\n\n  Output_A ──► K1:NC    (selected when K1 OFF = position A)\n  K2:COM ────► K1:NO    (selected when K1 ON)\n  Output_B ──► K2:NC    (selected when K2 OFF = position B)\n  Output_C ──► K2:NO    (selected when K2 ON = position C)\n  K1:COM ────────────────► T2 primary HOT\n\n  K1, K2 = Omron G6S-2-DC24 (DPDT relay)\n  D_fly1, D_fly2 = 1N4148 (flyback protection)\n  Q_relay1, Q_relay2 = BC184C (relay drivers)\n  R_relay1, R_relay2 = 1K (base resistors)\n\nSW_ABC (3-position rotary):\n  Pos 1 (A): K1=OFF, K2=OFF\n  Pos 2 (B): K1=ON, K2=OFF\n  Pos 3 (C): K1=ON, K2=ON\n\nOUTPUT TRANSFORMER:\n  T2 = JT-11ELCF (1:1)\n  Primary: from relay K1:COM\n  Secondary: → J3 XLR pin 2 (HOT), pin 3 (COLD)\n  Shield: → GND\n\nUse JT-11ELCF symbol from TripleTopoCustom library"
		(at 25.4 25.4 0)
		(effects (font (size 1.524 1.524)) (justify left))
		(uuid "f7000001-swch-text-0007-000000000001")
	)
)
